? PATTERN ? 63
The program can create symmetrical/reflective or anti-symmetrical/repetitive patterns, as well as simple checkered patterns, which can be generated using the repetitive option. The program will prompt the user whether the pattern should be symmetric or repetitive by asking the user to enter either 's' for symmetric, or 'r' for repetitive.
